#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2021-04-22-quarkus-2-0-0-alpha1-released.adoc:64
#, fuzzy
msgid "This release contains an Alpha implementation of Continuous Testing. This allows tests to be run in development mode, and can be enabled by pressing 'e' in the console (or through the Dev UI). If you enable testing, your test suite will be run once at the start, and then continuous testing will run your tests as you are coding, and tell you if your changes will break any tests. This will give you instant feedback on your changes, without having to switch to a browser. As much as possible we only run tests that are relevant to the code that has been changed."
msgstr "这个版本包含一个持续测试的Alpha实现。这允许测试在开发模式下运行，可以通过在控制台按'e'来启用（或通过开发用户界面）。如果你启用了测试，你的测试套件将在开始时运行一次，然后持续测试将在你编码时运行你的测试，并告诉你你的修改是否会破坏任何测试。这将给你的变化提供即时反馈，而不需要切换到浏览器。我们尽可能地只运行与被修改的代码有关的测试。"

